{"title":"Algorithm-Problem-组合数字","date":"2020-02-28T02:51:29.000Z","slug":"Algorithm-Problem-组合数字","comments":true,"updated":"2020-02-28T02:53:42.588Z","content":"<h3 id=\"问题描述\">问题描述<a href=\"post/Algorithm-Problem-组合数字#问题描述\"></a></h3><p>给定一个无重复元素的数组 candidates 和一个目标数 target ，找出 candidates 中所有可以使数字和为 target 的组合。</p>\n<h3 id=\"解决方法\">解决方法<a href=\"post/Algorithm-Problem-组合数字#解决方法\"></a></h3><p>回溯 + 剪枝</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">package main</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"fmt\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"string\">\"sort\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">func <span class=\"title\">dfs</span><span class=\"params\">(candidates []<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>, start <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>, end <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>, path []<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>, result *[][]<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>, target <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i := end; i &gt;= start; i-- &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tleft := target - candidates[i]</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tpath = append(path, candidates[i])</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> left == <span class=\"number\">0</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\ttemp := make([]<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>, len(path))</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tcopy(temp, path)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t*result = append(*result, temp)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tpath = path[<span class=\"number\">0</span> : len(path) - <span class=\"number\">1</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">continue</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> left &lt; <span class=\"number\">0</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tpath = path[<span class=\"number\">0</span> : len(path) - <span class=\"number\">1</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">continue</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tdfs(candidates, start, i, path, result, left)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tpath = path[<span class=\"number\">0</span> : len(path) - <span class=\"number\">1</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">func combinationSum(candidates []<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>, target <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>) [][]<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsort.Ints(candidates)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tlen := len(candidates)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tvar path []<span class=\"keyword\">int</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tvar result [][]<span class=\"keyword\">int</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tdfs(candidates, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, len - <span class=\"number\">1</span>, path, &amp;result, target)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">func main() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tcandidates := []<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&#123;<span class=\"number\">2</span>, <span class=\"number\">3</span>, <span class=\"number\">6</span>, <span class=\"number\">7</span>&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tret := combinationSum(candidates, <span class=\"number\">7</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Println(ret)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"Algorithm-Problem-根据身高重建队列","slug":"Algorithm-Problem-根据身高重建队列"},"next":{"title":"golang高并发实例","slug":"golang高并发实例"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/Algorithm-Problem-组合数字/"}